data.description: Adorable 2 story single family home built in 1895 on a corner lot. Original hardwood floors throughout, custom built-ins in the dining room and kitchen with original stain glass window in the entryway. Enjoy the property from the covered front porch, the large backyard with mature landscaping and fruit trees or newer covered side patio. Small attached garage that can be used for more storage, along with an unfinished basement. Property is being sold as-is, so cash and conventional only. Floor plan available. Mineral rights excluded. Call for a showing today!
